Package: edfkmeans
Type: Package
Title: Degrees of freedom and model selection for k-means clustering
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-07-27
Author: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: David Hofmeyr <dhofmeyr@sun.ac.za>
Description: Estimates the number of clusters for kmeans using the method of Hofmeyr, D. "Degrees of freedom and model selection for kmeans clustering", ArXiv (2018). Uses a generalisation of Stein's lemma to approximate the effective degrees of freedom for kmeans. This is then used within BIC to estimate the number of clusters present in the data.
License: GPL-3
Depends: Rcpp (>= 0.12.16)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
